results.description:
White Rock lake, Sunset Bay
Photo 1:  Those Seeds Look Delicious
This juvenile is eyeing a full stalk of delicious seeds.  Some of the red is peeking out.  There will be lots of red when it matures.
 Photo 2:  Yummy!
Munching on a seed.  Note the stripped seed stalk, he was eating a ton of them.
